  - CVE: no new HIGH. Microsoft.Kiota.Abstractions 1.21.2 HIGH is pre-existing baseline.
  - ADR-check: ADR-001/007/008/010/013/024/029/032 all clean — no new endpoints, no new
    interfaces, no new DI registrations, mapping layer single-choke-point preserved per
    inventory recommendation §6.2.
  - bff-extensions §A: no new packages; existing IDocumentDataverseService used (ISP-segregated
    per shared CLAUDE.md); test-update obligation §F satisfied (5 new tests across 2 files).

COORDINATION WITH PARALLEL SIBLING:
